# `NAMESPACE` MAWS.SyntaxEngine
A parser-ish sort of thing.

## `CLASS` MawsRequest.cs
Logic for MAWS Requests.

There will be more information about what MAWS Requests are here soon.

### `METHOD` GetDic()
TBD

#### Details
1. Get a nice name for the assembly, and create a trace log.
2. Split the MAWS Request into seperate components.
3. Return a dictionary that contains the MAWS Request components.
